    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Mix</strong> together the mustard, honey and mayonnaise with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> olive oil and a pinch of salt and pepper - this is your dipping sauce</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
